Subject: Re: [VB] RE: [T2] battery disconnect

2 batteries in series make 24 volts. 2 batteries in parallel make 12
volts. When parked and using camping gear, isolate the second battery
with a manual or automatic switch to prevent draining your main
battery for starting up when you are ready to go.

John
